The app uses **three coexisting styling approaches** with no unified strategy:

| Approach | File Count | Lines | % of Total |
|----------|-----------|-------|------------|
| **globals.css** (monolith) | 1 | 4,674 | 28.8% |
| **Plain CSS** (co-located) | 33 | 8,579 | 53.0% |
