### 7.2 Patterns Used

```typescript
// Centralized auth gate (migrated from boilerplate in V33)
const { supabase, user } = await requireAuth();

// Standard return type
{ success: boolean; error?: string; data?: T }

// Admin client for cross-user writes
const admin = getAdminClient();

// Background task (serverless-safe)
after(async () => {
  // notifications, activity events, achievement evaluation
});

// Cache invalidation
revalidatePath("/dashboard");

// Type safety: let TypeScript infer from the typed client
const { data } = await supabase.from("user_horses").select("*");
// data is automatically typed — never use `as unknown as`
```

